Class IPDetectorPluginManager

  freenet.node.IPDetectorPluginManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
ForwardPortCallback
public class IPDetectorPluginManager
extends Object
implements ForwardPortCallback

Tracks all known IP address detection plugins, and runs them when appropriate. Normally there would only be one, but sometimes there may be more than one.
